WnHmeaLRkwrL5Z4.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8KYmu5pWnHmeaLRkwrL5Z4.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Tefal)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt would be rude not to mention how good the Stewpot looks, too. It\u0026#39;s available in two colours, black and red, which is a long way from Le Creuset\u0026#39;s rainbow of shades.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHowever, the red is an absolute classic shade that looks at home in my neutral kitchen. It also features a gold handle which adds an on-trend touch to the traditional colours.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith the pull of the lightweight feature, I\u0026#39;m happy to sacrifice less colour options. But if you\u0026#39;d rather have more choice, here are a few more of \u003cem\u003eIdeal Home\u0026#39;s\u003c/em\u003e favourite cast-iron pots to choose from.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"ced47ffc-3dd6-48e1-8e1a-dd640b3973c0\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://john-lewis-and-partners.pxf.io/c/221109/871855/12148?subId1=idealhome-gb-1357342823774782088\u0026amp;sharedId=idealhome-gb\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.johnlewis.com%2Fjohn-lewis-cast-iron-round-casserole%2Fblue%2Fp4055471%3Fsize%3D21cm%26s_ppc%3D2dx_mixed_home_BAU%26tmad%3Dc%26tmcampid%3D2%26gad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCj0KCQjw-e6-BhDmARIsAOxxlxWmOP_XWXcI4JmqIaQAfzGqegPUZbDpFCLzZL5enUPSX_75q_c6QjQaAtwJEALw_wcB%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds\" data-model-name=\"Cast Iron Round Casserole, Blue, 21cm\" data-url=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/john-lewis-cast-iron-round-casserole/blue/p4055471?size=21cm\u0026amp;s_ppc=2dx_mixed_home_BAU\u0026amp;tmad=c\u0026amp;tmcampid=2\u0026amp;gad_source=1\u0026amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjw-e6-BhDmARIsAOxxlxWmOP_XWXcI4JmqIaQAfzGqegPUZbDpFCLzZL5enUPSX_75q_c6QjQaAtwJEALw_wcB\u0026amp;gclsrc=aw.ds\" target=\"_blank\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://john-lew